{
  "stem": "24111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because my father had this experience of imprisonment, and because my brother is two years older than me, at that time 19 years old, and because we, as a family, thought that they are the most-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the people in bigger danger, we decided they should-- they should go first.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans didn't want your father to remain to execute this transfer of funds and machinery?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very happy that my mother would be here doing that, because my mother worked--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--With my father in-- in the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- and my mother agreed to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had such details on individuals that if a guy came into the consulate or wherever, the-- the passport house, that they would know his business?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would know what he did, what he owned, what they wanted from him?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget my father had a registered business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the books were always under control of CPAs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Germans took the books-- when the-- took the business over, the books were available to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the records of export and import between Switzerland were-- were needed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The bank books were in their hands, not in ours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only need they had was signatures, actually, to transfer money, although time was necessary too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Machinery couldn't be shipped from day to the next.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unfortunately, what happened was that the war with Poland started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father and brother left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The war with Poland was in September of '39, and they left-- I would have to look it up exactly, but they left in March of '39, so they left a few months earlier.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
